game.name: Barbie Agent Team Dress Up
game.description:
Becoming an agent is a dream of Barbie for years. Luckily, she is going to take a chance to join a secret agent team in which her role is to spot all the bad souls of the society and send them behind the bars. Does it sound pretty interesting? But, before going on the mission, she needs to be dressed up as an agent. Will you help her out in picking up the suitable outfits? Join Barbie Agent Team Dress Up game and get ready to help the doll to make her dream come true! 
For this job, a kind of special costume is required to put on. Browse through all the options you see on the screen and pick up the ones that suit her personality the most in this brand new dressing game for girls! All the members of the team do not have an idea what they should choose, so they started arguing with each other. Now you are their last hope when it comes to sorting out this problem. Check out a wider array of exciting dresses and see what combination of outfits will help them look professional secret agents.
It is the first time when Barbie has got such a wonderful opportunity. Select the right special costumes and do not forget to change their overall look by giving them a new hairstyle in this html5 doll game! Complete their look with the selection of the appropriate shoes and weapons! Try to do your best to take care of the doll and her team of agents! Dress her up while keeping in mind that she is playing the role a leader of the spy squad! Plenty of outfits, accessories, and hairstyles to choose from in this free kids game to play online, no download required!
